OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FTransgender people can be  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbaptised, Vatican says     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Transgender people can be baptised in  
OL,6, the Catholic Church as long as doing so
OL,7, does not cause scandal or "confusion", 
OL,8, the Vatican has announced.             
OL,10,FThe Church's doctrinal office also said
OL,11,Ftrans people could be godparents at a  
OL,12,Fbaptism and witnesses at a wedding.    
OL,14,FThe move follows attempts by Pope      
OL,15,FFrancis to make the Church more        
OL,16,Fwelcoming to LGBT people.              
OL,18,FThe Pope told one trans person in July 
OL,19,Fthat "even if we are sinners, he (God) 
OL,20,Fdraws near to help us".                
